A space force is a military branch that conducts space warfare. Currently, one nation has had an independent space force, The Russia's space forces is an independent organisation (This Corps was existed from 1992 til 1997 and from 2001 to 2011, and reestablished on 2015 as a branch of the Russian Aerospace Forces). A space force is almost always a part of the air force, which may function as an air and space force or as an aerospace force, as the United States Air Force does.
